;; ========================================================================
;; §Z — PHASE VALIDATION CHECKLIST
;; ========================================================================
;;
;; Track which sections each phase is expected to unlock.
;;
;; Phase 0 (prerequisites):
;;   [x] §A all pass (existing relational baseline)
;;   [x] §B solver defs parse (B1-B6)
